{"type": "article", "id": 25074, "title": "金属怀表", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-07T07:11:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607123114QRMykDBLmjNZnJeX.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款怀表是给那些还习惯于看手表而不是手机的人，它带有明显的怀旧成分。金属表盘本身非常简洁，用长短线条刻痕来表刻度，只有时针和分针两个指示时间，并不十分精确或清晰，但能带给人更多的纪念意义。怀表直径 45 毫米，很小巧。有棕色和灰色两种，售价 165 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/mens-watches/axcent-pocket-watch/?v=79cba1185463\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123111eutgSsvQRJo5cWDC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.50854701\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123112mQDX2rlMdA1E7i6P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123112tJisnjE1o3QMdqgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91346154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123113NSwmhaZIqgLisrxF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92094017\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123114ZQYcnxvCqt0Fdi1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49679487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}